  <h1>BlazeMates Privacy Policy</h1>
  <p>Effective date: 2025-08-01</p>

  <h2>Information We Collect</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Profile info you provide (name, bio, preferences).</li>
    <li>Photos you choose to upload or capture for your profile.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>How We Use Information</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>To show your profile and enable matches and chat.</li>
    <li>To operate and improve the app’s features.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Data Sharing</h2>
  <p>We do not sell your personal information. We may share data with service providers (e.g., hosting) solely to provide the app.</p>

  <h2>Data Retention & Deletion</h2>
  <p>You can request deletion of your account and associated data from Settings → Delete Account, or by contacting us.</p>

  <h2>Contact</h2>
  <p>Email: support@yourdomain.com</p>
